---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 151
By: Plotinus
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=The Integral Effort Required
  - 975
  - 873
---
When therefore you seek to state or to conceive Him, put all else aside;
abstracting all, keep solely to Him; do not look for something to add,
rather you have probably not yet sufficiently abstracted from Him in your
conception.
